Path: Nushell
Content:
nibon7 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11324] added a new 
``ulimit``
 command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11273] simplified the 
``clear``
 implementation
KAAtheWiseGit 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11334] added a 
``format``
 base command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11293] replaced bash with POSIX sh in tests
AucaCoyan improved IDE support: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11320] :sparkles: Make 
``hover``
 equal to 
``help``
 command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11284] :recycle: Match 
``--ide-hover``
 with 
``help``
 command
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11317] fixed piping output logic
Hofer-Julian 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11315] moved 
``stor``
 commands to category 
``Database``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11308] move history into its own module
AntoineSebert 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11302] fixed a build error
sophiajt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11299] bumped the reedline dependency to 0.27
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11290] added a 
``nothing -> table``
 signature to 
``format date``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11157] disabled directory submodule auto export
CAESIUS-TIM 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11286] fixed a logical error in help glob
drbrain 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11285] added code to enforce that required, optional, and rest positional arguments start with an uppercase and end with a period
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11278] did the same for command usage
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11276] converted the remainder of ShellError variants to named fields
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11258] fixed replacement closures for 
``update``
, 
``insert``
, and 
``upsert``
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11229] added Polars struct support without unsafe blocks
CAD97 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10986] made a change to only run $env.PROMPT_COMMAND once per prompt
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11328] reverted lock file changes due to openssl build failure
, and did some version bump work (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11333] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11303] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11298] 3
)
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11340] reverted "Only run $env.PROMPT_COMMAND once per prompt"
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11339] updated reedline to improve resize behavior
